snippet.title: Mundaun - Now Available | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
Mundaun is now being published by Annapurna Interactive and is available now on PlayStation 5 for the first time. This new update includes 4K/60fps support on current-gen platforms, additional bug fixes, new languages, and more.

Mundaun is a lovingly hand-penciled horror tale set in a dark, secluded valley of The Alps. Explore various areas full of secrets to discover, survive hostile encounters, drive vehicles, fill your inventory, and solve a variety of handcrafted puzzles.

#ps5 #ps5games
